I don‚Äôt like the idea of invoking wscript from uninstaller. Windows Script Host may be disabled on some hardened PC.
Under HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows Script Host\Settings, create a new DWORD value named ‚ÄúEnabled‚Äù and set the value data to ‚Äú0‚Äù.
A pop up will show that ‚ÄúWindows Script Host access is disabled on this computer. Contact your administrator for details.‚Äù





